# Custom environment variables for claudebox containers.
# Copy this file to ~/.claudebox/env and fill in your values.
# Loaded by Docker via --env-file, so syntax is `KEY=VALUE` per line;
# blank lines and lines starting with `#` are ignored.

# --- Persistent settings (always loaded; not touched by toggle-provider.sh) ---

# Git identity used for commits inside containers. Without these, every new
# slot needs `git config user.email/name` set up by hand.
# GIT_AUTHOR_NAME=Your Name
# GIT_AUTHOR_EMAIL=you@example.com
# GIT_COMMITTER_NAME=Your Name
# GIT_COMMITTER_EMAIL=you@example.com
# EMAIL=you@example.com

# --- Provider settings (toggled by toggle-provider.sh) ---
# Lines between the START / END markers below are commented/uncommented in
# place by the toggle script. Don't move the markers; don't add `#__OFF__ `
# prefixes by hand (the script uses them to track which lines it disabled).

# === PROVIDER START ===
# Example: route through OpenRouter instead of Anthropic direct.
# ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=https://openrouter.ai/api
# ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=sk-or-v1-your-token-here
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_OPUS_MODEL=anthropic/claude-opus-4
# ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_SONNET_MODEL=anthropic/claude-sonnet-4
# ANTHROPIC_DEFAULT_HAIKU_MODEL=anthropic/claude-haiku
# === PROVIDER END ===
